***** Instructions for installing and running this game *****

* System requirements
	GNU Emacs with png-support
* Install
        If not existing, create ~/source (mkdir ~/source)
        copy the nummove.tar.gz to this directory
	untar/zip it (tar -xvvzf nummove.tar.gz)

* Try it out :)
	Start GNU Emacs
	Press ALT + X and type "load-file"
	Here you enter "~/source/nummove/nummove.el"
 	Again press ALT + X and type "nummove"
	Happy playing :D

